title: Polish Roads
message:
A map based on places that can be found in Poland (mainly southern regions)

The map idea is from 2015. In 2016 I started the research. I collected a lot of photos of real places in Poland. First, in-game versions of the map were created in late 2016. In 2017 I stopped the development of any mods. After a year of break, I created the project one more time from scratch. After 4 months of development, the map was released to the BeamNG repository. Overall the map is rather fictional with some known buildings. My goal was to fit Silesian voivodeship, with estates and countryside. I think the map has its own atmosphere, typical for post-communist countries.

[B]Map now includes:[/B]
- Custom assets (including: new buildings, shops inspired by real Polish brands, Polish road signs, custom roadside advertisements)
- Much better AI support
- Working traffic lights
- 3 bigger estates (all redesigned)
- Post-industrial area (redesigned)
- Countryside (redesigned)
- Bus station and railroad station (all redesigned)
- 3 new camping places
- Race/drift track
- Underground garages + garages with customizable interior
- Lots of farm fields
- Few easter eggs
- Train system support (still imperfect)
- LUA features
- New scenarios (including: races, rally time attacks, garage-to-garage missions )

- bus routes work, but they are not updated for the new map
